#to accept the length, breath of rectangle
#and display area nd perimeter in cm
length=int(input("enter the length of a rectangle: "))
breadth=int(input("enter the breadth of a rectangle: "))
area=length*breadth
perimeter=2*(length+breadth)
print(area ,"in cm")
print(perimeter ,"in cm^2")


o/p:
enter the length of a rectangle: 2
enter the breadth of a rectangle: 2
4 in cm
8 in cm^2
